Helena Barlow https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helena_Barlow 0 Helena Barlow (born 5 September 1998) is a former English child film and stage actress best known for her role as Rose Weasley in Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2. In 2012, she starred as young Estella in Mike Newell's Great Expectations alongside Helena Bonham Carter and Ralph Fiennes.
